column5: All these little underwater videos are great
You said it!!! Keep the underwater vids coming T.J., really entertaining to watch. Do you just use an Aquaview with a recording device?
Cool video TJ. Next time slow down the crank and you will catch that fish bud

I love the footy you've got, keep 'em coming.  I love them 'cause they show how the fish reacts, how far it chases, how it strikes.... lets me appreciate them more.  I think fishing is more than "hey mines bigger than yours!", more about the beauty of the animal.
Ya should of changed lures TJ..... it wasn't interested enough for a strike but pretty cool to watch Leechman

Yup.. an aqua vu and a recording device.. whne I originally did these I didnt bother capturing the misses... but later.. well they seem almost more interesting to me.  Ive go lots more coming, im trying to get one or two a day done, so I have a bunch more for the next few months.. then.. im gonna get some NEW stuff done!
